overview: Love Live! Sunshine!! Aqours 6th LoveLive! ~KU-RU-KU-RU Rock 'n' Roll TOUR~ (ラブライブ！サンシャイン!! Aqours 6th LoveLive! ～KU-RU-KU-RU Rock ‘n’ Roll TOUR～) (formerly Love Live! Sunshine!!
